verse.lines:
While living below,
everywhere that I go,
This world's full of trouble and pain;
There's murder and crime,
this is the end time,
When people are going insane;

This world is falling apart,
I'm so glad Jesus lives down in my heart;
I'm carried away in the Light of today,
As the world gets so dismal and dark;
While there's struggles
and troubles outside,
Something is stirring inside of the Bride;
As the world gets so dark
and it all falls apart,
I'm glad Jesus lives down in my heart.

They're praying for peace,
for the hostage release,
While holding a gun in their hand;
There's moral decay,
a great falling away,
In the shape this world's in
it won't stand;
